Fixed a functionnality bug that was preventing progress in other areas. A proper launch before July is too unrealistic, the estimates need to be pushed back to 2 weeks later. A lot of lessons are learned along the way !
Been away from Commeth these last few days but coming back strong and full of ideas ! Some new challenges arise and time passes very quickly. Commeth just wants to see the light of day already !

Code is being cleaned up and rearranged, this is refreshing and will make a smoother UX. The UI is getting better too. As for the logo, an idea has been found and it's in the works ! Doing everything to launch before the end of the month !
